resources.residConnectUpsellFlyoutText: O ka kgona go bona dinepe le dibidio didirišweng tša gago, ditirišong, le dinetwekeng tša setšhaba ka moka lefelong le tee.  Go thomiša, netefatša gore o kgokagantšwe inthaneteng.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_EmptySourceView: Dinepe tša gago ka moka di fihlilwe. Go bontšha tše dingwe, fetoša dipeakanyo tša gago.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_GenericDevice:
Tirišo ya dinepe e go bontšha dinepe le dibidio go tšwa go didirišwa tša gago ka moka ka lefelong le tee.

Go bona dinepe le dibidio go tšwa khomphutheng ye nngwe, eya go khomphutha yeo, eya go SkyDrive.com/windows go taonelouta le go hloma Microsoft SkyDrive, tsena ka akhaonte ya gago ya Microsoft, gomme o netefatše gore o kgetha Tšea difaele tša gago go tšw ago gongwe le go gongwe ga peakanyo.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Device: Ge e le gore o natšo, netefatša gore o šetše o di tsentše ka gare ga Diswantšho tša gago tša bokgobapuku bja {{%1}}.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Service: Tsenya dinepe tše dingwe ka akhaonteng ya gago go thomiša.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_SkyDrive:
SkyDrive e go fa bobolokelo bja dinepe bja mahala bja inthaneteng, bja dibitio le bja ditokomane gore o kgone go di fihlelela kae goba kae.

Eya go SkyDrive.com go thomiša. Dinepe le dibitio dife goba dife tše o di bolokago fao di tla bontšwa mo.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_PicturesLibrary:
Go thomiša, kgokaganya go sedirišwa (khamera, mogala, teraebe ya foleše ya USB, bjalobjalo.), o imphote goba o kopiše dinepe le dibidio ka bokgobapukung bja Diswantšho.

Ge e le gore o šetše o na le dinepe goba dibidio mo khomphutheng ye, netefatša gore di ka bokgobapukung bja gago bja Diswantšho. O ka laola bokgobapuku bja gago bja Diswantšho ka go Explorer ya Difaele.
